---
description: TypeScript conventions.
globs: types/**, components/**/*.types.ts, app/**/*.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

- Strict mode; no `any`; no non-null assertions outside generated code.
- Builder fields are `string | null`. `slug: string` always required.
- `import type` for type-only imports.
- Re-export library types via `VariantProps`.
- Always `@/` alias.
